    <title type="html"><![CDATA[Overriding the Maven local repository]]></title>
    <link href="http://blog.ccare.me/blog/2009/07/02/overriding-the-maven-local-repository/"/>
    <updated>2009-07-02T14:17:00+01:00</updated>
    <id>http://blog.ccare.me/blog/2009/07/02/overriding-the-maven-local-repository</id>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>Playing with Maven today - have been trying to establish a build from a clean repository (not .m2). Guessed that you could set the local repository, but took ages to find the prop...</p>

<pre><code>mvn -o install -Dsettings.localRepository=/var/tmp/m2
</code></pre>

<p>does the trick</p>
